commentary: Mominul Haque to Samuels, 1 run just in and that is a century! driven to backward point and they are away for a single, but that is a good throw from Gazi and Rahim whips the bails away...third umpire called. Thomas was diving at the striker's end and while his bat was in when the bails came off, there is a chance that the bat was in the air at the point when the bails were removed. A very tough call one way or the other, more so given the situation of the game. Given not-out in the end to get Samuels his century.

text: just in and that is a century! driven to backward point and they are away for a single, but that is a good throw from Gazi and Rahim whips the bails away...third umpire called. Thomas was diving at the striker's end and while his bat was in when the bails came off, there is a chance that the bat was in the air at the point when the bails were removed. A very tough call one way or the other, more so given the situation of the game. Given not-out in the end to get Samuels his century.

commentary: Mashrafe Mortaza to Thomas, FOUR runs edged and four! that was outside the off stump, he went out to fiddle at it, got an edge and flies between the keeper and the slip, goes to the fence to win West Indies the game
